text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ivanovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 749 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Ivanovka, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
